                                                  Problem Statement
In NITT for obtaining the transcript, degree, duplicate ID card,grade card,duplicate transfer certificate  the procedure is long .The candidate has to apply in person at the transcripts section of the Office of the Dean Academic for the issue of transcripts in the prescribed application available in the institute website along with the bank challan for payment of fee or by Demand draft . This procedure is lengthy so in place of this we can have online portal for this on which candidates can apply for their transcript and for their degree and the payment of fees can be make through online transaction no need to make fee payment through bank challan.This portal is also used for applying for duplicate ID card,grade card,duplicate transfer certificate  It can reduce the paper work.
